<img width="200px" class="rounded float-start pe-4" src="../img/difficulty/degree_difficulty.jpg">

I chose to major in MIS because of its mix of Information Technology and Business. With the digital world becoming increasingly intertwined with the business world, MIS graduates are high in demand. I saw this major as a valuable asset for me in opening up a wide range of career opportunities and career paths. 
